{"tid":232531,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"求救！深水埗區邊間診所比較好","createTime":"2017-05-06T19:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T20:10:17.000Z","uid":26763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c48aab2f6d2a157a12b39360493adb4f54b5db4","tid":232531,"uid":26763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:35:47.000Z","msg":"病左4日，燒足4日，最低37.3度，最高39.8度，去過公院同診所，兩次都話流感屌你老母，窮人條命賤我認，但等左勁撚耐就換黎2分鐘嘅斷症，而且食左咁耐藥可以話一啲用都無，真係好唔順氣<br />\n我上網睇過資料<br />\n啲症狀顯示有機會係扁桃線發炎而引起嘅發燒<br />\n請問各位巴絲，有無深水埗區嘅診所介紹下，最好有大概收法同電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e571778d1293410726edbdc808dbb390767188","tid":232531,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:37:28.000Z","msg":"冇打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇睇開的醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e158a90065a2e776947f416936e5a42c5b6cdbc","tid":232531,"uid":26763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:37:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>病左4日，燒足4日，最低37.3度，最高39.8度，去過公院同診所，兩次都話流感屌你老母，窮人條命賤我認，但等左勁撚耐就換黎2分鐘嘅斷症，而且食左咁耐藥可以話一啲用都無，真係好唔順氣<br />\n我上網睇過資料<br />\n啲症狀顯示有機會係扁桃線發炎而引起嘅發燒<br />\n請問各位巴絲，有無深水埗區嘅診所介紹下，最好有大概收費同電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b6ad41f2d1f92982976931e9733930e1aeb158ab","tid":232531,"uid":26763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:38:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇睇開的醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打左無用"},{"pid":"00823b52175cec56cc1df3ea6d80127dfa574396","tid":232531,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:40:48.000Z","msg":"你每日訓幾耐？<br />\n幾點訓<br />\n而家都唔訓？"},{"pid":"6e5a99acb0062d25c308134185d83bae0fda5082","tid":232531,"uid":5521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:42:18.000Z","msg":"急症"},{"pid":"fd910dc4953b4e0e47cb6fb7ea246783f23123a6","tid":232531,"uid":77171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:45:56.000Z","msg":"青山道尾 楊x寧都幾好 <br />\n去睇過一次 好有心機同我講解個病點引起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外睇開個間 長期好多人 睇幾分鐘就趕你走咁<br />\n不過啲藥幾好"},{"pid":"f22e5685e1657ee203b896e4959ba6540bc037d9","tid":232531,"uid":26763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:52:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你每日訓幾耐？<br />\n幾點訓<br />\n而家都唔訓？</blockquote><br />\n就係食左個診所醫生藥<br />\n食一次訓兩至三個鐘<br />\n依家已經食曬<br />\n痛到訓唔到<br />\n而且勁唔眼訓"},{"pid":"cc020263952e1ecafaeb89d6ec1b5fa140e5cea2","tid":232531,"uid":26763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>急症</blockquote><br />\n姐係公院<br />\n上面提左"},{"pid":"0792970a7769794f6fa80b5acc3b2e68f37edb8c","tid":232531,"uid":26763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:54:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>青山道尾 楊x寧都幾好 <br />\n去睇過一次 好有心機同我講解個病點引起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外睇開個間 長期好多人 睇幾分鐘就趕你走咁<br />\n不過啲藥幾好</blockquote><br />\n幾錢到？<br />\n兩間詳細地址？"},{"pid":"31fbec017cf5ee086fc0f1265510b29dd1136cac","tid":232531,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T19:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你每日訓幾耐？<br />\n幾點訓<br />\n而家都唔訓？</blockquote><br />\n就係食左個診所醫生藥<br />\n食一次訓兩至三個鐘<br />\n依家已經食曬<br />\n痛到訓唔到<br />\n而且勁唔眼訓</blockquote><br />\n夜晚最長果次訓幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個醫生成日同我講要早訓同埋訓耐d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話寧願下午唔訓 等夜晚早d同一次過訓好d"},{"pid":"76fc3bffdefcee5591e9268c11fcb9fdce3ecb16","tid":232531,"uid":26763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T20:10:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你每日訓幾耐？<br />\n幾點訓<br />\n而家都唔訓？</blockquote><br />\n就係食左個診所醫生藥<br />\n食一次訓兩至三個鐘<br />\n依家已經食曬<br />\n痛到訓唔到<br />\n而且勁唔眼訓</blockquote><br />\n夜晚最長果次訓幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個醫生成日同我講要早訓同埋訓耐d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話寧願下午唔訓 等夜晚早d同一次過訓好d</blockquote><br />\n我認我夜訓我衰<br />\n但係都訓得好足下<br />\n7個鐘以上"}]}